GIFAnim.mcc/MUIA_GIFAnim_Data

   NAME
    MUIA_GIFAnim_Data -- [I...], UBYTE *

   FUNCTION
    Here there may be directly supplied GIF data to avoid reading
    from a file.

    Note that if MUIA_GIFAnim_Data is used, MUIA_GIFAnim_DataSize
