    MUIA_GIFAnim_File

GIFAnim.mcc/MUIA_GIFAnim_Fallback

   NAME
    MUIA_GIFAnim_Fallback -- [I...], BOOL

   FUNCTION
    If set to TRUE and the file specified in MUIA_GIFAnim_File
    doesn't exist or it is not a GIF file, or the data supplied
    in MUIA_GIFAnim_Data are not valid, the object still setups
    and MUIA_GIFAnim_Invalid is set to TRUE .

    If set to FALSE and file specified in MUIA_GIFAnim_File
    doesn't exist or it is not a GIF file, or the data supplied
    in MUIA_GIFAnim_Data are not valid, the object refuses to
    setup.

    Default TRUE .

